00:11:24,060 --> 00:11:25,140
I even moved out.

257
00:11:25,140 --> 00:11:26,300
They don't need to know.

258
00:11:27,540 --> 00:11:28,300
Dingding.

259
00:11:29,060 --> 00:11:30,660
When we rescue lives,

260
00:11:31,300 --> 00:11:33,420
