277
00:12:01,420 --> 00:12:02,660
and you're starting to get picky.

278
00:12:02,660 --> 00:12:03,300
Listen to yourself.

279
00:12:05,420 --> 00:12:06,900
Uncle.

280
00:12:08,780 --> 00:12:11,020
Uncle.

