Did Yan put you up to this?

284
00:12:24,180 --> 00:12:25,380
How's she doing?

285
00:12:25,420 --> 00:12:26,180
Is she doing well?

286
00:12:26,380 --> 00:12:27,540
She's been fine lately.

287
00:12:27,540 --> 00:12:28,660
Rest assured, Uncle.

